    "title": "Sweet Winter Slaw",
    "description": "This salad will bring color to your winter dinner table and liven up any meal. You can leave out the caramelized macadamias, if you like, or use roasted peanuts instead. Consider serving the slaw with chard cakes or roast chicken.",
